pkgmetadata.longdescription: # Type stubs for django-huey[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-huey-stubs.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/django-huey-stubs)This package provides type stubs for the [django-huey](https://github.com/coleifer/django-huey) package.If you find incorrect annotations, please create an issue. ## Installation```shell script$ pip install django-huey-stubs```
